data.description: Solar lease paid for. This is a 4 bedroom with open floor plan for large gatherings. Kitchen has a large eating area with plenty of storage.  The master suite has a large walk in closet, and a bonus area that can be used as a nursery, workout room, craft room, office, or gaming area, including walk in closet. Master suite bath has separate shower and tub.  The other bedrooms all have very deep closets for extra storage.  Paid off solar lease with zero true up in the last 3 years per owner.  Great location, great schools, easy to show. Call your favorite agent to see asap.
